org.eclipse.ui.commands

Class KeyConfigurationEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.ui.commands.KeyConfigurationEvent
  • Deprecated. 
    Please use the bindings support in the "org.eclipse.jface" plug-in instead.

    @Deprecated
public final class KeyConfigurationEvent
extends Object
    An instance of this class describes changes to an instance of IKeyConfiguration.

    This class is not intended to be extended by clients.

    Since:
    3.0
    See Also:
    IKeyConfigurationListener.keyConfigurationChanged(KeyConfigurationEvent), SchemeEvent
